text: Kaif is a given name and a surname. Notable people with the name include: *Kaif Bhopali, Indian Urdu poet and lyricist *Katrina Kaif (born 1983), British film actress and model *Mohammad Kaif (born 1980), Indian cricketer ==See also== *Aivan-i-Kaif, city in and capital of Eyvanki District, Garmsar County, Semnan Province, Iran *Tel Kaif District, a district in Ninawa Governorate, Iraq *Tel Kaif, an Assyrian town in northern Iraq *Kaif al Mulk, a village in Guney-ye Markazi Rural District, East Azerbaijan Province, Iran
title: Kaif
